     C* G24: CHAIN by relative record number (no key). RRNFILE has
     C* records 11,22,33. CHAIN RRN 3 reads the 3rd (val 33). Exit 33.
     FRRNTRAN IP  F      80            DISK
     FRRNFILE IF  F      80            DISK
     IRRNTRAN    01
     I                                        1   10RRN
     IRRNFILE    02
     I                                        1   20RVAL
     C           RRN       CHAINRRNFILE              99
     C                     ADD  RVAL      RPGRET
     CLR                   SETOF
